{"tid":1261633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(還清白) 陳澤滔: 梁頌恆和黃之鋒也被嚴重抹黑","createTime":"2019-06-27T10:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:34:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":223,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6d349a1ca78aaf07e171061e5976d1b2fe46cf","tid":1261633,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156226262567793&amp;id=576952792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156226262567793%26id%3D576952792&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=16c949a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156226262567793&amp;id=576952792</a><br />\n<br />\nChan Chak To<br />\n6小時<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆搭的士走同黃之鋒阻人衝金紫荊應該係雨革後最成功嘅抹黑事件<br />\n<br />\n因為本身仇家多同埋有相有片更加令更多唔用腦（又或者明知但因為私怨而特登講）嘅朋友樂此不疲<br />\n<br />\n特此講第N 次<br />\n<br />\n1. 梁頌恆走係因為清場，事實係在場嘅知名人士當中，佢係留到最後果個。留到咁夜係因為大家都叫極唔走，公開咁講又會俾人屌散水，只能個別咁勸。點解你唔會見到其他議員搭的士走？因為佢哋通常都十二點前走咗<br />\n(又因為咁，喺呢度特別讚揚尋晚譚文豪同楊岳橋🙇&zwj;♂️）<br />\n如果果晚有cam 影住其他示威者（包括我），你會見到有人搭巴士走有人搭van 仔走。<br />\n<br />\n2. 黃之鋒果朝根本好晏先嚟，佢哋係排公眾觀旗果邊入，背向旗桿雙手交叉好似係行為藝術，同阻人無關。<br />\n事實人鏈事件係喺四五點果時發生。基本上示威者由凌晨已經喺度拗衝唔衝入去，而最後係得唔到共識。<br />\n警方防線同金紫荊其實有幾百米路程，中間仲有一大堆水馬，衝唔衝到其實好難講，但就一定唔關學民事囉。<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩次都喺現場，唔係親眼所見都唔敢幫人澄清"},{"pid":"d1e4f2a24b9c1c757fd3fbbe6ee4b9d77eabaabb","tid":1261633,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290a53e7fa2abf70db22d0417fbb28d734b29cae","tid":1261633,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2672c17a2b8d4fd1d86ba3c59eca34167f71066","tid":1261633,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842d464697a80851a3e50a6b9e2d3590107719c7","tid":1261633,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8021af83636b997443cbf187297ca018a78c1b","tid":1261633,"uid":42846,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"學民仔張XJAPAN，真係傳得太多就冇人敢面對事實，張相太方便易用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72114874722a5e2dea3546f5692a14f0f935c3f","tid":1261633,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e158d33107491c46137488d8334bccc757ef5670","tid":1261633,"uid":144113,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"諗起今朝呢度啲人拎梁搭的士張舊gif屌佢琴晚走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1bda3afa73d0d8a0cd8306351a7ea50a611ae1","tid":1261633,"uid":14517,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"終於解決到x japan歷史懸案"},{"pid":"56eccffc4ad2e37b38ec28a41cb0e64c7ae2c586","tid":1261633,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c47e7eba66bba6e2105772efb6d88d598f0be4","tid":1261633,"uid":4783,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"e158d33107491c46137488d8334bccc757ef5670","tid":1261633,"uid":144113,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"諗起今朝呢度啲人拎梁搭的士張舊gif屌佢琴晚走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"個陣明明佢係make sure全部人走哂先搭的士走<br />\n唔係就佢俾人拉啦<br />\n得罪講句，個陣其他議員都走哂，得返佢<br />\ncut佢搭